Detailed Description

cvmx_sli_ctl_status

This register contains control and status for SLI. Write operations to this register are not ordered with write/read operations to the MAC memory space. To ensure that a write has completed, software must read the register before making an access (i.e. MAC memory space) that requires the value of this register to be updated.
